## ServersApi

### Place Server Order
## Place Server Order
POST https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/servers/order
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

