### Place Buy Now Server Order
## Place Buy Now Server Order
POST https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/servers/order/buy_now_server
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

{
 "server_id": "<number>",
 "server_hostname": "<string>",
 "server_root_password": "<string>"
}


### Update Reverse DNS
## Update Reverse DNS
POST https://my.interserver.net/apiv2/servers/{{id}}/reverse_dns
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
Accept: application/json
Cookie: sessionid={{cookieKey}}
X-API-KEY: {{apiKey}}
sessionid: {{apiKey}}

{
 "ips": "<string>"
}


